      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779717901275,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Core entities:\n    - task\n    - job\n    - user",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Core entities:\n    - task\n    - job\n    - user",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "wnDO7_k6xQSt6C8Z_u2c3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 11507.635553745718,
      "y": 222.0981230995776,
      "width": 730.259033203125,
      "height": 325,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5J",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 225682280,
      "version": 344,
      "versionNonce": 2088713576,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779718875267,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "API:\n    - users should be able to create/schedule a job(immediate, future,  recoccuring)\n    POST /api/v1/jobs -> jobId\n    Headers: JWT | userSession\n    body: {\n        taskType (SendEmail, ...)\n        schedule \n        params\n    }\n\n    - users should be able to monitor the status of the jobs\n    GET /api/v1/jobs?status&time&page&size-> Job[]\n    Headers: JWT | userSession",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "API:\n    - users should be able to create/schedule a job(immediate, future,  recoccuring)\n    POST /api/v1/jobs -> jobId\n    Headers: JWT | userSession\n    body: {\n        taskType (SendEmail, ...)\n        schedule \n        params\n    }\n\n    - users should be able to monitor the status of the jobs\n    GET /api/v1/jobs?status&time&page&size-> Job[]\n    Headers: JWT | userSession",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "nWSICTKQuVDEuRZAN_HtC",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 11503.623472206922,
      "y": 588.9606348527074,
      "width": 444.07940673828125,
      "height": 150,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5K",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 134968344,
      "version": 337,
      "versionNonce": 1039154280,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779718876550,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Data flow:\n    1. Users schedule a job\n    2. Persist this job in DB\n    3. Job picked up and executed at schedule time\n        - if failed, retry with exponention backoff\n    4. Update the job status ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Data flow:\n    1. Users schedule a job\n    2. Persist this job in DB\n    3. Job picked up and executed at schedule time\n        - if failed, retry with exponention backoff\n    4. Update the job status ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
