      "text": "Queue ordered by execution time:\n    - ❌  Kafka doesn't has delivery delay feature\n    - ✅  Redis Sorted Set\n    - ✅  RabbitMQ with delivery delay feature\n    - ✅✅  SQS - delivery delay, retries, dead letter queue, high available, visibility timeout",
